%% Diagram: Capacity Planning Workflow
%% Type: flowchart
flowchart TD
    A["Frame objectives<br/>and falsifiable hypotheses"] --> B["Model workload mix<br/>and scenarios"]
    B --> C["Prepare systems<br/>and realistic data or mocks"]
    C --> D["Warmup then validate<br/>steady-state behavior"]
    D --> E["Execute scenarios<br/>and observe SLO signals"]
    E --> F{"Bottleneck or<br/>SLO violation?"}
    F -->|Yes| G["Classify bottleneck<br/>and isolate variables"]
    G --> H["Remediate or refine model"]
    H --> D
    F -->|No| I["Derive capacity envelope<br/>from saturation points"]
    I --> J["Apply headroom to<br/>targets and risk budget"]
    J --> K["Report decisions, limits,<br/>and operational follow-ups"]
